Scribble Tools for Eclipse
==========================



Building from source
--------------------

First task is to obtain and build the parent pom used by jbosstools.

Create a suitable folder and run:

	svn co http://anonsvn.jboss.org/repos/jbosstools/branches/3.3.indigo/build/

Then go to the 'build' folder and run:

	mvn clean install

This will only need to be done first time, or when the local maven repository is cleared out. In the future this parent pom may be added to a central maven repository, so that this step is no longer required.

The next step is to go to the root folder of the scribble-tools-eclipse repository, and run:

	
